examples.en: The unthinkable happened  I passed the exam.
It is unthinkable that a mistake like this could have happened.
It is unthinkable that they will ever make such an offer.
It would be unthinkable for me to stay anywhere but with the family.
In some parts of the city nearly unimaginable opulence can be found side by side with nearly unthinkable poverty.
To most people it seemed unthinkable that such a gentle man could be guilty of such awful crimes.
